ygData.messageBody:
Cazic Thule is great place for FS weapons....even if you aren't tough enough
to fight there, you can always walk in and ask if anybody is selling. Most
people are overweight in there with FS so you should be able to pick one up
pretty cheap, 5 or so plats. If you are on Veeshan server look me up, I
usually have one on me, and I'll be in Cazic for another week or so.

Salr D'Taynkk
Dark Warrior of The Kith
Veeshan
